text: Dejan Jekovec (born 22 August 1974) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Slovenia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tržič
